title: Poro rider sej already removed?
body: winter wonder skins still up but sejs winter skin has already been removed :( i just got funds into my paypal after all the blasted paypal off days (dec 23rd I put in the request).  I understand today is the end of snowdown, but is it possible to remove them all at the same time? or add sejs skin back to the store until everything is ready to come down.

replies.body: I just check it out, and I'm seeing Sej, Ori and Malz in the store. Let me know if you're still seeing the issue. :]
Send in a ticket to support, that will probably work better.
